OL,3,CGuernsey financial consultant
OL,4,Cknowingly worked for 'alleged war
OL,5,Ccriminal'
OL,7,FThe unnamed man is described as "high-
OL,8,Frisk" and "an alleged war criminal"
OL,9,Fwhom Ms Blondel continued to provide
OL,10,Fservices for until March 2020, despite
OL,11,Fknowing this and that he was under
OL,12,Finvestigation for money laundering.
OL,14,FOn one occasion the investigation
OL,15,Funcovered that she received one
OL,16,Fmillion euros into her personal bank
OL,17,Faccount from a company owned by
OL,18,F"Client 1" to set up a proposed
OL,19,FGuernsey trust company.
