OL,7,FMs Blondel was found to have breached
OL,8,Flaws in Guernsey by carrying out
OL,9,Fregulated activities without a licence
OL,10,Fand failing to have the required
OL,11,Fpolicies, procedures and controls in
OL,12,Fplace to manage the risk of providing
OL,13,Fservices to these clients.
OL,15,FGabriel Vedrenne, Senior Reporter at
OL,16,FACAMS moneylaundering.com, has been
OL,17,Flooking at Ms Blondel as part of an
OL,18,Finvestigation into the issue.
